%% I2 — Sequence diagram: POST /transactions (B4 FastAPI)
%% Source: tasks/i2-end-to-end-flow-trace/artifacts/flow-trace.md
%%
%% Path A: direct HTTP (pytest, curl)
%% Path B: reviewer UI via Vite proxy (/api/b4/service/transactions)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(240, 248, 255) Path A — Direct HTTP
        participant Client as Client<br/>(curl / TestClient)
        participant Uvicorn as Uvicorn ASGI<br/>port 8766
        participant FastAPI as FastAPI app<br/>main.py
        participant Pydantic as TransactionCreate<br/>schemas.py
        participant Handler as create_transaction()<br/>main.py:28-30
        participant Store as TransactionStore.create()<br/>store.py:25-39
        participant Memory as _records list<br/>store.py:18-19
    end

    Client->>Uvicorn: POST /transactions<br/>JSON body
    Uvicorn->>FastAPI: ASGI HTTP request
    FastAPI->>Pydantic: parse and validate body

    alt invalid payload (amount ≤ 0, bad type, etc.)
        Pydantic-->>Client: 422 Unprocessable Entity
    else valid payload
        FastAPI->>Handler: create_transaction(payload)
        Handler->>Store: store.create(payload)
        Store->>Memory: append TransactionRecord<br/>_next_id += 1
        Memory-->>Store: ok
        Store-->>Handler: TransactionResponse
        Handler-->>FastAPI: TransactionResponse
        FastAPI-->>Client: 201 Created + JSON
    end

    Note over Client,Memory: Path B — Reviewer UI (optional entry)

    participant Browser as B4FastApiDemo<br/>handleSubmit
    participant Vite as Vite B4 proxy<br/>vite-plugin-b4-api.ts
    participant Spawn as startServer()<br/>spawn uvicorn

    Browser->>Vite: POST /api/b4/service/transactions
    Vite->>Spawn: ensure uvicorn on :8766
    Spawn-->>Vite: health ok
    Vite->>Uvicorn: proxy POST /transactions
    Note right of Uvicorn: Steps 2–11 same as Path A
